1990;;The Big Man;;British;;David Leland;;Kenny Ireland, Liam Neeson;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Big_Man;;A Scottish miner (Liam Neeson) becomes unemployed during a union strike. He is unable to support his family and cannot resolve his bitterness about his situation. Desperate for money, he accepts an offer made by a Glasgow gangster to fight in an illegal bare-knuckle boxing match. A long and brutal fight follows.